Package fang2.transformers

Class SpinTransformer

java.lang.Object
fang2.core.TransformerAdapter
fang2.transformers.SpinTransformer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Transformer
Direct Known Subclasses:
SpinAccelerationTransformer
public class SpinTransformer extends TransformerAdapter
A "spinner" TransformerAdapter. This transformer turns the sprite according to the angular velocity set in the transformer. Treats it as constant velocity.
